<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idef76e338-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db" identifier="/us/usc/t54/s100501"><num value="100501">§ 100501.</num><heading> Areas included in System</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The System shall include any area of land and water administered by the Secretary, acting through the Director, for park, monument, historic, parkway, recreational, or other purposes.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idef76e339-3a70-11f1-83cd-8a39f388f6db">(<ref href="/us/pl/113/287/s3">Pub. L. 113–287, § 3</ref>, <date date="2014-12-19">Dec. 19, 2014</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/128/3098">128 Stat. 3098</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
